Season: 1953
BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablesr/rio8rcm53.html
* Torneio Octogonal Rivadavia Corrêa Meyer 1953, tournament successor of Copa Rio held in 1951 and 1952.
* Note: Uruguayan FA didn't allow the participation of Nacional.  Fluminense (Brazil) takes its berth.

